      "value": "<p>Cost: 16 Creation Points</p><p>Drain: 15 CCD Chakra</p><p></p><p>As a reaction when you would be hit with a ranged attack you spend the CCD Drain of this enhancement to twist the attack around your body, redirecting it back at your target. </p><p>Make a ranged taijutsu attack with your A.Ts contested by your target's attack roll. </p><p>If your attack roll is higher the attack automatically hits your attacker, and it deals an additional 2 dice of damage.</p>",
